			<strong>Others licenses:</strong>
			Some entries may cite text, images or resources from external sources. Their original licenses
			apply, and I indicate the authors if known.
		</p>
	</section>
	<section>
		<h2 id="colophon">Colophon</h2>
		<p>
			<strong>Typography:</strong> I mainly use
			<a href="https://googlefonts.github.io/ebgaramond-specimen/">EB Garamond</a> by Georg Duffner,
			a beautiful free and open-source serif typeface based on the 16th century designs of
			<a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Garamond_(police_de_caract%C3%A8res)"
				>Claude Garamond</a
			>. In code snippets, I use
			<a href="https://monaspace.githubnext.com/">Monaspace</a> by GitHub Next, a beautiful open-source
			monospace superfamily with texture healing. And finally, annotations are set in
			<a href="https://yourownfont.com/shop/product/abby/">Abby</a> by "Your Own Font Foundry", a cute
			handwriting typeface (not free).
		</p>
		<p>
			<strong>Technologies:</strong> This website is built with <a href="https://astro.build/"
				>Astro</a
			>, I wrote a bit about this static website generator in a dedicated
			<a href="/2023/launching-blog-astro">blog entry</a>. Notable dependencies include
			<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/">Tailwind CSS</a> for styling,
			<a href="https://github.com/expressive-code/expressive-code">expressive-code</a> for code blocks,
			<a href="https://github.com/lovell/sharp">sharp</a> for image processing, and
			<a href="https://github.com/francoischalifour/medium-zoom">medium-zoom</a> for image zooming.
		</p>
		<p>
			<strong>Inspiration:</strong> A mishmash of inspiring links, in alphabetical order,
			<a href="https://aureliendossantos.com/">Aur√©lien Dos Santos</a>,
			<a href="https://www.edwardtufte.com/">Edward Tufte</a>,
			<a href="https://erika.florist/">Erika</a>,
			<a href="https://gwern.net/">Gwern Branwen</a>,
			<a href="https://100r.co/">Hundred Rabbits</a>,
			<a href="https://kalele.io/blog/">Kalele (Vaughn Vernon)</a>,
			<a href="https://sinja.io/">OlegWock</a>,
			<a href="https://pilcrowonpaper.com/">Pilcrow</a>,
			<a href="https://practicaltypography.com/">Practical Typography</a>,
			<a href="https://staffeng.com/">StaffEng</a>,
			<a href="https://press.stripe.com/">Stripe Press</a>,
			<a href="https://lethain.com/">Will Larson</a>.
		</p>
	</section>
	<section>
		<h2 id="changelog">Changelog</h2>
		<p>An historic of this website, its new features and page redesigns, with examples.</p>
		<Changelog />
	</section>
</Layout>
